long_description: Use the Kabeltek high-carbon steel Flexweave cable to protect your bike and other equipment against thieves. This woven cable is made from high-carbon steel with brass; stronger then most other cables on the market that use grey aircraft-grade steel. Aluminum swaged ends are strong and durable. Not to be used for towing. Must purchase lock separately.
